creator: Music App Developers
descriptionHtml:
Using the Music Writer app you can compose, create and edit sheet music on your phone.

Editing the score,
- Add, remove and edit notes on two independent layers
- Change time signature, key signature and clef for individual measures
- Add expression, articulation, slur and repeats to the sheet music
- Add lyrics to your music
- Add grace notes and tuplets
- Add or remove staffs
- Copy, paste or remove parts of the score

Playing the music,
- Set the playback volume on individual staffs
- Mute individual staffs, or set the playback to solo
- Show or hide individual staffs
- Set the tempo, and play the score

Exporting the sheet music,
- Save the sheet music to your phone
- Export the sheet music to PDF, MIDI, MusicXML and MWD. MWD files can be used to backup, share, or import your scores on other devices
descriptionShort: Create and edit sheet music quick and easy. Compose music on your phone.

container.value: Music App Developers, 26-28 Hammersmith Grove, London, W67BA

creator: Music App Developers
descriptionHtml:
Using Music Writer you can compose, create and edit sheet music on your phone or tablet.

Editing the score,
- Add, remove and edit notes on two independent layers
- Change time signature, key signature and clef for individual measures
- Copy, paste or remove parts of the score
- Change the instrument for a staff
- Add expression, articulation, slur and repeats to the sheet music
- Add lyrics to your music
- Add, remove or reorder staves
- Set title, subtitle and composer
- Show or hide tempo marking
- Support for grace notes and tuplets
- Support for multi-page, single-page or horizontal layouts
- Support MIDI connection to an external device

Playing the music,
- Set the playback volume on individual staves
- Mute a staff, or set the playback to solo
- Show or hide individual staves
- Set the tempo and play the score

Export / Import,
- Save the score to your phone
- Export the sheet music to PDF, MIDI, MusicXML or MWD
- Import MIDI and MusicXML
- MWD files can be used to backup, share, or import your scores on other devices
descriptionShort: Create and edit sheet music quick and easy. Compose music on your phone.
